ign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">滾滾洗衣君(conan)</span> 说: 人類一生平均七八十年才生一兩個繁殖力夠弱了吧。</q></div>人类因为有了文明有了科学才这么强的，一般的动物要形成种族优势都需要靠繁殖力，就像烧不尽的野草，灭不完的老鼠<br>而且人类的繁殖力并不弱，人类的繁殖成功率是所有动物中最高的，不过这也是靠了先进的医学"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/05/41/54176.jpg","floor":"#8-5","id":"1267729","time":"2017-7-29 13:24","userId":"light_44","userName":"lighthouse","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">君寻</span> 说: 这个主要原因是刷尾负鼠繁殖能力太强吧，繁殖能力弱的物种不太可能造成生物入侵现象</q></div>是它们在那里完全没有天敌，并从当中破坏了食物链<br><br>北极熊破坏食物链的话肯定是从顶层的"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/32/46/324634.jpg","floor":"#9","id":"1267694","time":"2017-7-29 10:34","userId":"kylecalloway","userName":"吉良吉影想要过平静的生活","userSign":"(Bites the Dust)","message":"<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/23735341\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">企鹅有句mmp要讲</a>","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/27/35/273543.jpg","floor":"#10","id":"1267700","time":"2017-7-29 10:56","userId":"hydrilla","userName":"黑藻","userSign":"(黑藻并非藻类！)","message":"这个帖子让我想起来看过这本<a href=\"https://read.douban.com/ebook/8876745/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">南极姑娘</a>","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#11","id":"1267733","time":"2017-7-29 13:34","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"会冷死的吧","sub":[]}]